

# Project `lib` directory

This directory contains project-specific libraries for StepperController (limit switches version).
Each library should be placed in its own subdirectory under `lib/`.

Example:
```
lib/
  ├── MyStepperLib/
  │   ├── src/
  │   │   └── MyStepperLib.h
  │   │   └── MyStepperLib.cpp
  │   └── library.json  # optional
```

PlatformIO will automatically compile and link these libraries.
See PlatformIO documentation for details:
https://docs.platformio.org/page/librarymanager/ldf.html
